This is a Stock Management System that can take care of your basic Inventory Management Needs.

Feature:

Display Stock Inventory
Buy Stock
Sell Stock
Delete Stock
Search Stocks from Your inventory

Currently Working On:
    Feature that are to be added
        File Storage
            -> So Data can be reused after every session
        Multiple Users
        Statistical Analysis
            -> Total Inventory value
            -> Total Sales
            -> Total Items in an inventory
            -> Change in Item Price Over time
        More Changable Stock Stocks
            -> Update Name
            -> Update Quantity
            -> Update Price
        Multiple Devices Support


DataTypes
Hash Table
Items:
    Quantity: int
    Price: Float
